390
00:24:40.490 --> 00:24:41.490
Ugh.

391
00:24:45.537 --> 00:24:47.119
Ji Soo, kau kemana?

392
00:24:47.983 --> 00:24:50.970
Lalu kenapa Kang Shin Woo 
