00:26:31.748 --> 00:26:33.848
Bagaimana kau tahu jam berapa
alarm kebakaran berbunyi?

430
00:26:33.848 --> 00:26:36.226
Pak Kang adalah satu-satunya 
orang di sekolah saat itu!

431
00:26:36.770 --> 00:26:38.022
Itu...

432
00:26:42.766 --> 00:26:44.048
Hei, Han Ji Soo.

433
00:26:45.535 --> 00:26:46.935
Tadi malam...

434
00:26:46.935 --> 00:26:50.132
Pak Kang dan aku terkunci di balik
gerbang tahan api bersama...

435
00:26:50.132 --> 00:26:53.488
Jika kita dikurung di sana bersama
-sama, aku pasti sangat bosan.

436
00:26:54.203 --> 00:26:55.353
Benar?

437
00:26:56.492 --> 00:26:58.734
Saat aku berkeliling mencari saksi.

438
00:26:58.734 --> 00:27:00.535
Kukatakan pada orang-orang
kapan alarm berbunyi.

439
00:27:01.105 --> 00:27:03.603
Terima kasih, Sherlock Holmes.
